name: VersionCueSyncStatus
shortdesc: The synchronization status of the file in Version Cue.

property.name: FILE_DOWNLOADED
property.shortdesc: The project version of the file was downloaded to the local workspace.

property.name: FILE_UPLOADED
property.shortdesc: The local version of the file was uploaded to the project.

property.name: FILE_NO_CHANGE
property.shortdesc: The synchronization resulted in no change because the local and project versions were identical.
